{
  "texts": [
    "To ensure comprehensive results, we conducted both multi-document and singledocument topic extraction.",
    "The latter approach allowed us to preserve the source of each document.",
    "Finally, we generated a Similarity Matrix of clustered topics to evaluate the consistency of documents, identify outliers, and establish a baseline for manual category composition.",
    "This method was adopted to derive categories for our taxonomies, and we provide the code used for these experiments.",
    "Methodology for coding research goals, research methods, and stakeholders in Sect. 4The initial methodology involved a general qualitative interpretative process."
  ]
}